Ms Carney has been receiving ‘hate mail’ since the incident from people who believe ‘Tebowing’ was banned by Principal Wicks for religious discrimination, which was ‘very unsettling’ for her.

‘It's a shame that people out there are so ready to judge when they weren't there to see what happened,’ she told ESPN New York.

