Recently-divorced skier Vonn, 27, last week joined the craze that mimics Tebow of NFL team Denver Broncos - and she had asked his brother beforehand if it would be OK to pull off the pose if she won.

Before stepping on the top step of the podium at the post-race ceremony to celebrate her 46th World Cup win, she dropped to a knee with her skis in her hand and pulled a ‘Tebow’ move.

Out of respect for Tebow she asked his brother, who was at the race, if it would be disrespectful, and he gave her the green light to do it. The two have recently struck up a friendship but deny dating.

